itle":5,"searchDepth":51,"depth":51,"links":86},[],[88],{"_path":89,"_dir":90,"_draft":6,"_partial":6,"_locale":5,"title":91,"description":92,"author":93,"dates":94,"image":96,"body":97,"_type":53,"_id":209,"_source":55,"_file":210,"_extension":57},"/blog/my-first-project-with-kirby","blog","My First Project with Kirby","this is a small description about me for my blog alsdfaldfs alsdfkasfd","@bruno",{"published":95},"2024-04-030","/inclousion.webp",{"type":10,"children":98,"toc":201},[99,106,120,127,132,138,145,150,156,161,196],{"type":13,"tag":100,"props":101,"children":103},"h1",{"id":102},"launching-my-first-project-with-kirby-cms-a-unique-rapid-development-experience",[104],{"type":18,"value":105},"Launching My First Project with Kirby CMS: A Unique, Rapid Development Experience",{"type":13,"tag":14,"props":107,"children":108},{},[109,111,118],{"type":18,"value":110},"I'm excited to share my latest project, ",{"type":13,"tag":21,"props":112,"children":115},{"href":113,"rel":114},"https://www.inclousion.ch/",[25],[116],{"type":18,"value":117},"Inclousion.ch",{"type":18,"value":119},", where I ventured into new territories with Kirby CMS, enhanced by the utility-first approach of Tailwind CSS and the simplicity of Alpine.js.",{"type":13,"tag":121,"props":122,"children":124},"h2",{"id":123},"introduction-to-the-project",[125],{"type":18,"value":126},"Introduction to the Project",{"type":13,"tag":14,"props":128,"children":129},{},[130],{"type":18,"value":131},"This project marked my first experience with Kirby CMS. Kirby offers a flexible, file-based CMS that eliminates the need for a database, which intrigued me from the start. I decided to pair it with Tailwind CSS for styling and Alpine.js for the minimal interactive components, aiming for a lean and efficient tech stack.",{"type":13,"tag":121,"props":133,"children":135},{"id":134},"development-experience",[136],{"type":18,"value":137},"Development Experience",{"type":13,"tag":139,"props":140,"children":142},"h3",{"id":141},"kirby-cms",[143],{"type":18,"value":144},"Kirby CMS",{"type":13,"tag":14,"props":146,"children":147},{},[148],{"type":18,"value":149},"Kirby's learning curve was steep yet rewarding. Its no-database, file-driven approach made it exceptionally straightforward to setup and deploy. The CMS's panel is intuitive, allowing me to manage content flexibly without relying on traditional database constraints.",{"type":13,"tag":121,"props":151,"children":153},{"id":152},"lessons-learned-and-conclusion",[154],{"type":18,"value":155},"Lessons Learned and Conclusion",{"type":13,"tag":14,"props":157,"children":158},{},[159],{"type":18,"value":160},"This project was an excellent first foray into using Kirby CMS. It provided a fast development cycle, thanks to the combined power of Kirby, Tailwind CSS, and Alpine.js. Each tool offered its unique strengths:",{"type":13,"tag":162,"props":163,"children":164},"ul",{},[165,176,186],{"type":13,"tag":166,"props":167,"children":168},"li",{},[169,174],{"type":13,"tag":170,"props":171,"children":172},"strong",{},[173],{"type":18,"value":144},{"type":18,"value":175}," for its simplicity and flexibility in content management.",{"type":13,"tag":166,"props":177,"children":178},{},[179,184],{"type":13,"tag":170,"props":180,"children":181},{},[182],{"type":18,"value":183},"Tailwind CSS",{"type":18,"value":185}," for its speed and utility-first design philosophy.",{"type":13,"tag":166,"props":187,"children":188},{},[189,194],{"type":13,"tag":170,"props":190,"children":191},{},[192],{"type":18,"value":193},"Alpine.js",{"type":18,"value":195}," for its minimalist approach to adding interactivity.",{"type":13,"tag":14,"props":197,"children":198},{},[199],{"type":18,"value":200},"Overall, this project not only enhanced my skills but also added a unique piece to my portfolio. For fellow developers considering this tech stack, I highly recommend diving in; it's well worth the learning curve!",{"title":5,"searchDepth":51,"depth":51,"links":202},[203,204,208],{"id":123,"depth":51,"text":126},{"id":134,"depth":51,"text":137,"children":205},[206],{"id":141,"depth":207,"text":144},3,{"id":152,"depth":51,"text":155},"content:blog:my-first-project-with-kirby.md","blog/my-first-project-with-kirby.md",1713471514490]